Usage: getSdpGroupAttribute [-help] [-flip] [-justifyBy] -name <string>
                            [-orient] [-origin] [-padding] [-skipSpace] [-type]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-flip              # Get the flip information of sdp object (bool, optional)
-justifyBy         # Get justifyBy of sdp object (bool, optional)
-name <string>     # Name of sdp object (string, required)
-orient            # Get the orient information of sdp object (bool, optional)
-origin            # Get location of sdp object (bool, optional)
-padding           # Get padding of top sdp object (bool, optional)
-skipSpace         # Get the space pattern in sdp object (bool, optional)
-type              # Get type of sdp object (bool, optional)